p://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9981248499307901, \"rank\": 0.001878672771746346, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999867472981, \"rank\": 1.272871801837499e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That it was Saint Lucia's first Olympic medal only made the moment sweeter.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel honored just to be an ambassador for my country,\\\" Alfred told reporters.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not many people know about Saint Lucia.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I can be in an Uber and they ask me where I am from\\u2026and they will be like 'Where's Saint Lucia?'\\\"\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are David-and-Goliath stories to be found across anyOlympicsbut perhaps few of the proportion of Saint Lucia versus the United States - or Jamaica.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David-and-Goliath\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999867472981, \"rank\": 1.272871801837499e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saint Lucia, an Eastern Caribbean island nation, had never previously had an athlete on the Olympic podium while Americans have won well over 300 titles in athletics alone, topping the all-time medal table by a massive margin.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999996275221986, \"rank\": 3.723845877528998e-07, \"text\": \"Saint Lucia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alfred, 23, got herself in the right mindset by watching videos of retired Jamaican great Usain Bolt on Saturday morning and by the evening had catapulted herself into her country's own pantheon of greats.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999997882687464, \"rank\": 2.1173138026811211e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[I was] hoping that they could get their first Olympic medal and it came as a goal, so I am sure they are celebrating right now,\\\" said Alfred, who grew up running barefoot in a country that lacked proper track facilities.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels amazing to be honest.\\\"\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alfred will also compete in the 200m in Paris, with the first round set for Sunday, August 4.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999919402853, \"rank\": 8.059787048046365e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": []}]}"